      "officialTitle": "A Phase 2, Double-Blind, Multicenter, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled Trial Evaluating Fosfomycin/Tobramycin for Inhalation in Patients With Cystic Fibrosis and Pseudomonas Aeruginosa"
